per seat, revenue growth decelerates to 15% by 2027.
The tell: management uses the word 'seats' 14 times on
the earnings call and never mentions 'consumption' or
'usage-based.' That language pattern predicts the
business model problem 2 years before it shows up
in reported numbers."
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
```

